OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the day with scattered showers,
OL,7,Fthese will die out for a time. Cloud
OL,8,Fincreasing overnight with more showers
OL,9,Farriving from the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FIt will be another day of
OL,12,Fbright spells and showers, some
OL,13,Fperhaps heavy and thundery.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,16,FCloudy with rain or drizzle on
OL,17,FThursday. Bright spells and scattered
OL,18,Fshowers on Friday. A few showers at
OL,19,Ffirst on Saturday, otherwise dry with
OL,20,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
